text: Double Impact is a 1991 crime drama and action-adventure movie. It is about twin brothers involved with crime and secrets. Jean-Claude Van Damme plays the brothers Chad and Alex. The movie received negative reviews from the movie critics. Despite that, the movie was #2 at the box office.
